#MEM id=pre-dev-delivery-planning source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/skills/marketplace/pre-dev-delivery-planning/SKILL.md
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|name: ring:pre-dev-delivery-planning
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|description: |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Gate 9 (Full Track) / Gate 4 (Small Track): Delivery roadmap and timeline planning.
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Transforms tasks into realistic delivery schedule with critical path analysis,
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|resource allocation, and delivery breakdown. MANDATORY gate for both workflows.
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Tasks passed Gate 7 validation (Full Track) OR Gate 3 (Small Track)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Need realistic delivery timeline with dates
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Ready to convert tasks into delivery schedule
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Team composition known or determinable
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Tasks not validated → complete task breakdown first
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Proof-of-concept without delivery commitment
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Research/exploration work without delivery deadline
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|**Runs before:** ring:dev-cycle
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|**Runs after:** ring:pre-dev-task-breakdown, ring:pre-dev-subtask-creation
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Every roadmap must be grounded in reality, not optimism. Tasks not validated, team composition unknown, or start date absent → STOP and gather the missing input before proceeding.
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Phase | Activities |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning||-------|------------|
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **1. Input Gathering** | Load tasks.md; ask user for start date, team composition, delivery cadence, period cfg, velocity multiplier |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **2. Dependency Analysis** | Build dependency graph, identify critical path, find parallelization opportunities |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **3. Capacity Planning** | Calculate team velocity (custom multiplier), allocate resources, identify bottlenecks |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **4. Delivery Breakdown** | Group tasks by cadence (sprint/cycle/continuous), calculate period boundaries, identify spill overs, map parallel streams |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **5. Risk Analysis** | Flag high-risk dependencies, add contingency buffer (10-20%), define mitigations |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **6. Gate Validation** | Verify all tasks scheduled, critical path correct, dates achievable, period boundaries respected |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|When will the team start? Format: YYYY-MM-DD
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|How many developers? Options: 1 (solo), 2 (pair), 3-4 (squad), 5+ (large team)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Options: Sprints (1-2 weeks), Cycles (1-3 months), Continuous (no fixed intervals)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Duration: 1w, 2w, 1mo, 2mo, 3mo
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- Start date: YYYY-MM-DD
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Option | Multiplier | Example |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning||--------|-----------|---------|
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Minimal validation | 1.2x | 4h AI → 4.8h adjusted |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Standard validation ← recommended | 1.5x | 4h AI → 6.0h adjusted |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Deep validation | 2.0x | 4h AI → 8.0h adjusted |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Heavy rework | 2.5x | 4h AI → 10.0h adjusted |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Custom | user-specified | — |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|```
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|adjusted_hours = ai_estimate × multiplier
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|calendar_hours = adjusted_hours ÷ 0.90
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|calendar_days  = calendar_hours ÷ 8 ÷ team_size
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|task_days      = calendar_days + taura_days
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Where:
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|ai_estimate = from tasks.md (AI-agt-hours)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|0.90        = capacity utilization (AI agt standard)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|taura_days  = 0 (dev/Delivery) | 5 (Quality) | 10 (Quality integration)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|```
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|For each task, check: `task_end_date <= period_end_date`
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- If yes → fits completely (✅)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- If no → spill over (⚠️): allocate days split across periods
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Continuous delivery: no period boundaries — tasks scheduled by dependency and capacity only.
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|1. Build dependency graph from tasks.md
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|2. Calculate Earliest Start Date (ESD) per task
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|3. Calculate Latest Start Date (LSD) without delaying project
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|4. Tasks where ESD = LSD → on critical path (zero slack)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|MUST gen both:
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- `docs/pre-dev/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.md` — human-readable
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|- `docs/pre-dev/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.json` — machine-readable (see schema below)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|**Topology-aware paths:**
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Structure | Files Generated |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning||-----------|-----------------|
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| single-repo | `docs/pre-dev/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.{md,json}` |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| monorepo | Index + per-module `{module.path}/docs/pre-dev/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.{md,json}` |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| multi-repo | Per-repo `{repo.path}/docs/pre-dev/{feature}/delivery-roadmap.{md,json}` |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|```json
