M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|1. `dates.startDate` and `dates.endDate` REQUIRED — not null
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|2. `tasks` array MUST have ≥1 item
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|3. Every task MUST have `id`, `description`, `aiEstimate`, `adjusted`, `calendar`, `days`
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|4. `confidenceScore` MUST be 0-100
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|5. `milestones` MUST have ≥1 item
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|6. `criticalPath.taskIds` MUST reference valid task IDs
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|7. `version` MUST be `"1.0.0"`
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|8. `milestones[].taskIds` and `spillOvers` MUST reference valid task IDs
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|9. `velocity.teamSize` > 0
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|10. `cycleCapacity` MUST be present with all 5 fields
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|11. `cycleCapacity.availableDays` = `grossDays - bugBufferDays`
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|12. `cycleCapacity.slackDays` = `availableDays - allocatedDays` (negative = over-committed → add risk)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|13. `tasks[].phase` ∈ `{dev, quality, delivery}`; `tauraDays` must match: 0 for dev/delivery, 5 or 10 for quality
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|14. Continuous cadence: `periodDuration` = null, `periodStartDate` = null, milestones type = `milestone`, spillOvers = `[]`
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Category | Requirements |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning||----------|--------------|
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **Input Completeness** | Start date, team composition, cadence, period config (if sprint/cycle), velocity multiplier all confirmed |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **Dependency Analysis** | Graph built, critical path identified, parallel streams defined, no circular deps |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **Capacity Planning** | Velocity calculated, resources allocated, bottlenecks identified, ≤80% utilization |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **Delivery Breakdown** | Periods match cadence, boundaries calculated, spill overs identified, delivery goals measurable |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **Risk Management** | High-risk deps flagged, buffer added (10-20%), mitigations defined |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| **Timeline Realism** | No best-case assumptions, critical path validated, dates achievable |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|**Gate Result:** ✅ PASS → Ready for execution | ⚠️ CONDITIONAL (adjust) | ❌ FAIL (rework)
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Factor | Points | Criteria |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning||--------|--------|----------|
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Dependency Clarity | 0-30 | All mapped: 30, Most clear: 20, Ambiguous: 10 |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Capacity Realism | 0-25 | Realistic (70-80%): 25, Optimistic (90%+): 10, Undefined: 0 |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Critical Path Validated | 0-25 | Full graph: 25, Partial: 15, Assumptions: 5 |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|| Risk Mitigation | 0-20 | All flagged + mitigated: 20, Some: 10, None: 0 |
M|pre-dev-delivery-planning|Score 80+: proceed with confidence. 50-79: flag assumptions. <50: resolve unknowns before committing dates.